  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_0' aria-label=\" Mission Accessibility versus Union of India & Ors. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('0','2025','2025_12_443_454','2025INSC1376'); ><font size='4'> <strong>MISSION ACCESSIBILITY<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>UNION OF INDIA & ORS. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 12 S.C.R. 443</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 1376</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010006782025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration In the instant petition, the petitioner sought for the modification of the timeline for scribe registration in the Civil Services Examination conducted by Union Public Service Commission and for permitting the use of laptops equipped with Screen Reader Software along with papers for eligible candidates. Headnotes&dagger; Rights of Persons with Disabilities Act, 2016 &ndash; Constitution of India &ndash; Arts.14, 19, 21 &ndash; Enforcing the rights of persons with disabilities to equal opportunity &ndash; Measure of inclusivity &ndash; Modification of the timeline<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 03-12-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> WRIT PETITION (CIVIL) No. 206/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Disposed off</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_12_443_454','2025INSC1376','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class